Mewtwo (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0149: Dragonite
Pokémon
#0151: Mew →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Mewtwo (TCG Pocket).

Mewtwo has been featured on 48 different cards since it debuted in the Base Set of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Mewtwo cards are normally Psychic-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Mewtwo

Mewtwo
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
